  • Constructor Details

    • StargateClientNode

      public StargateClientNode(String nodeName, String apiRestUrl, String apiGraphQLUrl, String grpcHostName, int grpcPort)
      Full fledge constructor for a node. The host is not enough as a stargate node could have a load balancer on top of it changing the default host:8082...
      Parameters:
      nodeName - node identifier
      apiRestUrl - rest Api URL http://localhost:8082
      apiGraphQLUrl - graphQL Api URL, eg http://localhost:8080
      grpcHostName - grpc hostname
      grpcPort - grpc port
